0 FOCUS~
Syntax: focus <power rating> <ammount>
Example: focus speed 150

Focus lets you spend power to increase your speed, strength or aegis.
If you spend more than your rating, the energy is wasted.
~

0 STRENGTH~
This saiyan power rating enhances the damage dealt in combat.
~

