0 TELEPORT~
Syntax: teleport <target in area>
Example: teleport yurimaru

Mazoku can traverse short physical distances with incredible speed
by temporarily ducking back into the astral, and moving toward a
recorgnized target in the astral plane.  This costs essense, but
