0 RETIREMENT~

As Chaosium ages, people come and go.  Character even come and go,
as their players find themselves preferring different or new classes.
As a means of preserving some of Chaosium's history, and a reward for
serious pkillers, I'm making available the option of retiring characters.

Retiring a character removes them from play, for an indefinate period
of time.. perhaps retired chars may be allowed to come out of retirement
years from now, but not until then.  When a player retires, their record
will be added to a Chaosium hall of fame helpfile.  Their character will
also be immortalized in a hall of fame area, depending on their record,
reputation, play time, presense.. etc.. this can range from a statue and
plaque to a mobprogged mobile.

Requirements for retirement:
500 pkills.
Created six months or more ago.
500 hours played.
Full maxed status (SSJ, Shaolin, Runelord, Warlock/Archmagus/Ryozoku, Demonic)
500 primal

Btw, the 500 primal is to cut down on my workload.  Since, after all,
I need to do the ABing to carry this out.
~

0 SPEND TOKEN~
Syntax: spend <option>
Example: spend Weapons2

Tokens are granted by the admin as a reward for winning events
and turning in bugs.  They are shown on the score command, and
are non-transferable.

Spend is used to exchange tokens for various rewards.  These
include increasing some stances or weaponskills to 200, gaining
experience, and other such niceties.

Type spend with no argument to see an up to date list of rewards.
~


